Develop an Android App that can be used as a point-of-sale system (without the barcode scanning). 
On the activity interface provide buttons associated with each item bought (maximum four). 
The number of button clicks corresponds to the quantity of the item bought. 
The app should show the quantity of each item bought the total to be paid for each item, 
the grand total amount to be paid, 
a 15% discount and 
the net amount to be paid.
